  "title": "MARKETING   MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><p>•\tContinually meeting or exceeding sales quotas.</p><p>•\tSupervising and guiding the sales team as well as providing incentives to motivate staff to achieve sales targets.</p><p>•\tMonitoring the performance of the sales team.</p><p>•\tEnsuring that the store is clean and well-maintained at all times.</p><p>•\tBuilding and maintaining good working relationships with customers.</p><p>•\tIdentifying opportunities and strategies to increase sales.</p><p>•\tRegularly attending sales meetings and training sessions.</p><p>•\tEnsuring that the store is adequately stocked with company products.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>•\tProven experience in sales and customer service.</p><p>•\tProficient in all Microsoft Office applications.</p><p>•\tThe ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>•\tExcellent problem-solving skills.</p><p>•\tStrong management and leadership skills.</p><p>•\tEffective communication skills.</p><p>•\tExceptional customer service skills.</p><p></p>",
